---
title: Foolproof Greek-Style Chicken & Potato Salad with Almonds & Parmesan
description: Feeling like something fresh and tasty, low-carb and easy? May we present our Greek-style chicken seasoned in garlic. Tender and simply yum, resting on top of a crisp salad, sprinkled with cheese and garnished with almonds, this dish is perfect to ring in these warmer days (or any day for that matter)!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
